title: TDP-4 | Community Call (s0cc4) | $RETOKEN Launch Party | Wed 7p EDT / 08Sep2021
body:
# Overview
To celebrate all the efforts that have occurred to get our DAO SaaS / Framework created allowing us to vote on proposals, etc.  We are wanting to showcase these systems to the community at large and give our community members the opportunity to engage through voting with $RETOKEN.
> NOTES:
> * (only $RETOKEN that have been distributed thus far were done for [TDP-1 | Tokenomics Working Groups #1-3](https://snapshot.org/#/retokendao.eth/proposal/QmaRC6fsdoTs5Fuv6T9Pt7qkFEeo72LZ448Y5rnikjjYgS))
> * By holding $RETOKEN you are agreeing to the token policy as outlined within [RIP-1 | Genesis Proposal (Season 0)](https://snapshot.org/#/retokendao.eth/proposal/QmdJUQkW6dNWfuT5BZbx1qWzopgbpEFom1xaVsVCQCT7UD)

# The Proposal
1. reward 25 $RETOKEN for participating in tomorrow's important community call
2. reward 75 $RETOKEN (3x normal) for the hosts of the community call (with limit of 3 hosts)

## Hosts for Community Call (s0cc4)
* [yonks.eth Ξ Jason Younker](https://twitter.com/Yonks)
* [Ryan](https://twitter.com/rynstones1)
